'''阿卜杜勒·拉希德·萨利姆·萨尔曼·汗'''（{{lang-en|Abdul Rashid Salim Salman Khan}}，{{bd|1965年|12月27日|catIdx=S}}），被称为'''萨尔曼·汗'''（{{lang-en|Salman Khan}}），[[印度|印度]]知名演員、節目主持人、製片人、慈善家。 他是知名劇作家[[薩利姆·汗|薩利姆·汗]]（穆斯林）之長子，母親為莎瑪·蘇希拉·查拉克（Salma Sushila Charak/印度教徒），繼母[[海倫_(演員)|海倫·潔拉格·理察森]]（Helen Richardson/公教基督徒）為知名舞者及演員，有兩名弟弟[[阿巴斯·汗|阿巴斯·汗]]（Arbaaz Khan）與[[索哈爾·汗|索哈爾·汗]]（Sohail Khan），兩名妹妹阿維拉·汗（Alvira Khan）與阿皮塔·汗（Arpita Khan/收養的），另有兩名義結的乾妹<ref>[http://www.hindustantimes.com/Entertainment/Tabloid/I-don-t-want-more-sisters-Salman-Khan/Article1-1054357.aspx I have four sisters already-two of my own and two rakhi sisters] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130606034750/http://www.hindustantimes.com/Entertainment/Tabloid/I-don-t-want-more-sisters-Salman-Khan/Article1-1054357.aspx |date=2013-06-06 }}. Hindustan Times. 2013/5/3.</ref>阿米塔·卡克（Amrita Kak）<ref>[http://www.dayafterindia.com/magz_detail_news.php?id=866 Sallu standing for Rakhi Sister Amrita Kak] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140324110906/http://www.dayafterindia.com/magz_detail_news.php?id=866 |date=2014-03-24 }}. The Day After. 2011/7/15.</ref>與許維塔·羅希拉（Shweta Rohira）<ref>[http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2013-06-03/news-interviews/39713536_1_salman-khan-pulkit-samrat-bittoo-boss My fiancee Shweta Rohira is his rakhi sister] {{Wayback|url=http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2013-06-03/news-interviews/39713536_1_salman-khan-pulkit-samrat-bittoo-boss |date=20130608082643 }}. The Times of India. 2013/6/3.</ref>。薩爾曼為半穆斯林、半印度教徒<ref>[http://www.zimbio.com/Bollywood+Movies/articles/BOkyw5mDd_L/Half+Hindu+Half+Muslim+Says+Salman+Khan I am half Muslim and half Hindu]{{dead link|date=2018年4月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}. Zimbio. 2010/3/17. </ref>，整個家庭每年都會一起慶祝三大宗教的節慶<ref>[http://businessofcinema.com/news/god-one-galaxy-salman-khan/50914 In Galaxy, God is one, though our paths to reach the almighty are different]. Business of Cinema. 2012/9/20. </ref>。

==簡介==
[[寶萊塢|寶萊塢]]三汗天王之一的薩爾曼（另兩汗分別為[[阿米爾·汗|阿米爾·汗]]/Aamir Khan與[[沙魯克·汗|沙魯克·汗]]/Shahrukh Khan）在學生時代是冠軍游泳健將，曾代表印度出賽<ref>[http://movies.ndtv.com/bollywood/10-things-you-didn-t-know-about-salman-khan-308109 He was a swim champ at school and even tipped to represent India]. NDTV. 2012/12/27.</ref>。熱衷於健身，每天總花數小時鍛鍊<ref>[http://fitnessanddefense.com/salman-khan-workout/ Workout Routine and Fitness Secrets] {{Wayback|url=http://fitnessanddefense.com/salman-khan-workout/ |date=20130809231257 }}. Fitness And Defense. 2012/2/4.</ref>，為寶萊塢健身風氣的始祖<ref name="well toned">[http://www.pardaphash.com/news/bollywood-sexy-hunks-hrithik-roshan-shahid-kapoor-john-abraham-salman-khan/716620.html He is the man behind who started the trend of having a well toned body] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130730051155/http://www.pardaphash.com/news/bollywood-sexy-hunks-hrithik-roshan-shahid-kapoor-john-abraham-salman-khan/716620.html |date=2013-07-30 }}. Pardaphash. 2013/6/24.</ref>。他在拍攝《伙伴2007》的期間開始遭受三叉神經痛的困擾，直至2011年才前往美國治療<ref>[http://www.indianexpress.com/news/salman-khan-leaves-for-us-for-nerve-surgery/839382/ The actor is suffering from Trigeminal Neuralgia]. The Indian Express. 2011/8/30.</ref>。後續又發現腦部存有動脈瘤，無法再如往常般從事大量的健身運動與重量訓練<ref> [http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2013-01-11/mumbai/36279305_1_salman-khan-trigeminal-neuralgia-health-condition The Aneurysm is still there and it cannot be operated or scooped out]. The Times of India. 2013/1/11. </ref>，以致不再健美如昔，但卻仍是寶萊塢體格最健美的男星之一<ref name="well toned"/>。受母親影響，意外發掘出繪畫天份<ref> [http://www.bollywoodmantra.com/news/salman-khan-s-secret-talent-painting/1369/ Salman Khan's secret talent-Painting]. Bollywood Mantra. 2006/10/28.</ref>。出社會工作後，父親致贈了一條鑲了土耳其石的銀質手鍊給他<ref> [http://www.retailjewellerindia.com/Salman_Khan%E2%80%99s_lucky_blue-stone_bracelet_custom_designed_by_Anmol_Jewellers_Mumbai-25-308 Salman Khan's lucky blue-stone bracelet custom designed by Anmol Jewellers]{{dead link|date=2018年4月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}. The Retail Jeweller.</ref>，此後這條手鍊一直不離其身，甚至也經常在他的電影裡出現<ref name=" trademark">[http://www.theiconicstores.com/en/blog/2013/5/being-human-salman-khan-way The Salman Khan way]{{Dead link|date=2020年2月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}. Iconic. 2013/5/26.</ref>。

