===幕後===
薩爾曼是寶萊塢極少數樂於助人的人士<ref>[http://tribune.com.pk/story/166406/ill-share-my-income-with-bollywood-workers-salman-khan/ I'll share income with Bollywood workers]. The Express Tribune. 2011/5/12.</ref>、不少新人演員的導師與幕後才幹人士的推手，他自走紅以來，一直不吝給予機會啟用並指導新人演員，幫助他們在業界立足。希里克·羅山（Hrithik Roshan）與[[賽伊夫·阿里·罕|賽伊夫·阿里·罕]]（Saif Ali Khan）最初的健身教練就是薩爾曼<ref>[http://www.motleyhealth.com/celeb/the-workouts-of-salman-khan-a-bollywood-legend He also got both Saif Ali Khan and Hrithik Roshan stated with weight training and fitness]. Motley Health. 2012/4/13. </ref>；當三大汗之一的沙魯克·汗夫妻剛到[[孟買|孟買]]發展初期時，就是棲身於他的住所<ref>[http://entertainment.oneindia.in/bollywood/features/2012/rare-pictures-shahrukh-salman-khan-journey-friends-foes-100318.html It was Salman who helped him and his wife by providing a roof over their heads]. Oneindia. 2012/10/14.</ref>。業界人士都知道，只要有困難，去向薩爾曼求助就對了<ref>[http://entertainment.oneindia.in/bollywood/features/2013/salman-khan-being-human-to-friends-new-comers-114715.html He is the man who doesn't even think twice to help]. Oneindia. 2013/7/20.</ref>。

