==慈善事業==
[[File:Chillar_Party_kids_with_Salman_Khan.jpg|thumb]]
出自於積善之家<ref>[http://www.indicine.com/movies/bollywood/salman-khan-to-send-2500-water-tankers-to-marathwada/ Helping out people in need has been an inherent trait in the family]. Indicine. 2013/5/7.</ref>，受其雙親的影響<ref name="Help">[http://gulfnews.com/life-style/people/salman-khan-on-making-people-smile-1.1040762 Making people smile]. Friday magazine.2012/6/29.</ref>，薩爾曼一直有顆柔軟的心，他不斷幫助Deeds公益信託<ref>[http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=r-Pke5kxNiE Salman Khan shows his support towards our NGO DEEDS Public Charitable Trust]. Deeds India.</ref>，並時常探訪與陪伴孤兒院、特殊教養院的孩子以及醫院病童，且資助他們<ref>[http://salmankhanholics.com/post/11963310849/salman-his-secret-passion-beingsalmankhans Well-hidden secrets]. Cineblitz. June 2000.</ref> <ref name="associated"> [http://www.bollykings.com/philanthropic-bollywood-stars/ He is also closely associated with several other organizations]. Bollykings. 2011/12/24.</ref>。後來在前女友索米·阿里創建NGO行動的啟發下<ref>[http://www.indiatimes.com/bollywood/somy-ali-inspired-%E2%80%98being-human-name-salman-55946.html Somy Ali inspired 'Being Human' name]. India Times. 2013/1/18.</ref>，他也開始決定用自己的錢，登記設立了正式的基金會。

「'''心懷人性-薩爾曼·汗基金會'''（Being Human-The Salman Khan Foundation）」於2007年7月28日設立，旨在為弱勢群體提供教育與醫療保健方面之必要協助<ref>[http://www.beinghumanonline.com/ Spreading education and healthcare for the underprivileged] {{Wayback|url=http://www.beinghumanonline.com/ |date=20180929135721 }}. Being Human Online.</ref>。財源主要來自於銷售「心懷人性基金會」專有商品（金幣/手錶/服飾配件）所獲得的權利金<ref>[http://businesstoday.intoday.in/story/celebrity-marketing-actor-salman-khan-as-brand-endorser/1/193099.html Branded for life]. Business Today. 2013/4/14. </ref> <ref>[http://businesstoday.intoday.in/story/bollywood-actor-salman-khan-interview-being-human-foundation/1/193661.html My vision is to make the concept of giving accountable]. Business Today. 2013/3/28.</ref>
<ref name="noble cause">[http://www.fashionunited.in/news/fashion/being-human-to-launch-kids-wear-060820135849 Stands out for its positive, simple, human message] {{Wayback|url=http://www.fashionunited.in/news/fashion/being-human-to-launch-kids-wear-060820135849 |date=20130809131803 }}. Fashion United. 2013/8/6.</ref>、旗下製片公司電影票房獲利的分紅（電影製作由薩爾曼出資，但所有衍生的收益歸屬基金會）<ref>[http://www.indianexpress.com/news/skbh-productions-to-do-charity/800979 The money which I make through production will go for charity]. The Indian Express. 2011/6/9. </ref> <ref> [http://www.firstpost.com/bollywood/salman-khans-next-project-as-producer-feel-good-low-budget-films-608256.html The money that goes into production isn't the foundation's money]. Firstpost. 2013/1/31.</ref>、薩爾曼本人除了片酬與節目主持酬勞以外的所有收入<ref>[http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HCJWMF_VpM0 My endorsement earnings go to Being Human Foundation]. Business of Bollywood.</ref> <ref>[http://www.hindustantimes.com/Entertainment/Tabloid/Log-karein-toh-charity-main-karun-toh-publicity-Salman-speaks-out/Article1-913061.aspx I'm contributing five percent of everything I earn] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121016044331/http://www.hindustantimes.com/Entertainment/Tabloid/Log-karein-toh-charity-main-karun-toh-publicity-Salman-speaks-out/Article1-913061.aspx |date=2012-10-16 }}. Hindustan Times. 2012/8/13.</ref>；其餘零星來自於大眾捐助、慈善球賽門票收入、拍賣（薩爾曼本人的畫作<ref>[http://www.indianexpress.com/news/salman-khan-to-auction-his-paintings-for-charity/564111/ Salman Khan to auction his paintings for charity]. The Indian Express. 2010/1/6.</ref>/健身器材<ref>[http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2010-09-20/news-interviews/28244601_1_auctions-salman-khan-gym Salman Khan auctions gym session]. The Times of India. 2010/9/20.</ref> <ref>[http://businessofcinema.com/videos/salman-khan-auctions-his-cycle-for-being-human/41200 Salman Khan auctions his cycle for Being Human]. Business of Cinema. 2011/3/21.</ref>）等。他的下一步是準備開設連鎖餐飲店，以籌集更多資金<ref name="Open">[http://movies.ndtv.com/bollywood/salman-khan-to-open-restaurants-and-hospitals-319248 Open restaurants and hospitals]. NDTV. 2013/1/18.</ref>；最終極的目標是要讓基金會能夠自給自足，不必依賴任何外界財源<ref>[http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2013-01-17/news-interviews/36393522_1_salman-khan-stardom-fades-trust I really want to make the trust self sufficient]. The Times of India. 2013/1/17.</ref>；未來還計劃建醫院<ref name="Open"/>、蓋特殊教育學校<ref>[http://thepeninsulaqatar.com/saturday-editions/198570-a-star-with-a-conscience.html Salman Khan plans to open school]{{dead link|date=2018年4月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}. The PENINSULA. 2012/6/22.</ref>。

基金會自成立數年來，除了不斷宣揚其'''愛'''、'''關心'''、'''幫助'''、'''分享'''等 "心懷人性" 的核心理念<ref>[http://hindi.jagranjunction.com/2010/03/11/salman/ The biggest gift in the world you can give to anyone is to be human]. Jagran Junction. 2010/3/11.</ref>（這些會為人們帶來'''希望'''與'''喜悅'''<ref name="noble cause"/>）與實踐相關活動<ref name=" Help"/>以外，諸如鼓舞殘疾人士、為病童與貧童安排電影特映/節慶禮物/不定期探訪等<ref name="laugh"/>，也與不同機構建立長期伙伴關係<ref name=" Help"/> <ref name="associated"/>。在醫療保健方面－基金會協助印度骨髓捐贈資料登記宣導、青光眼宣導、自閉症宣導、資助先天性心臟病童的醫療手術費、為聽障兒童提供輔具或治療、在各地設立免費眼科醫療營、捐贈儲水槽給馬哈拉斯特拉邦受旱地區應急（缺水會造成衛生問題）；在教育方面－為農村青年之就業發展提供培訓課程、資助貧童就學、捐贈電腦給學校與孤兒院、提供免費或販售學前教育影片等，使得不少人受益，因而受到了整個印度社會的肯定<ref name=" Help"/> <ref> [https://www.facebook.com/BeingHumanOnline Being Human events].Being Human Online-Facebook.</ref> <ref>[http://www.glamsham.com/movies/scoops/13/apr/17-news-salman-khan-in-company-of-george-clooney-matt-damon-021306.asp In company of George Clooney & Matt Damon] {{Wayback|url=http://www.glamsham.com/movies/scoops/13/apr/17-news-salman-khan-in-company-of-george-clooney-matt-damon-021306.asp |date=20130602105720 }}. Glamsham. 2013/4/17.</ref>。

「心懷人性基金會」在2012年與2013年連續兩年的品牌信任報告裡被列為印度最值得信賴的[[非政府組織|非政府組織]]（the Most Trusted NGO in India）<ref> [http://thebrandtrustreport.wordpress.com/ The Most Trusted NGO in India]. The Brand Trust Report. 2013/2/6.</ref>。

